<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id122ecb42-e3ef-11ef-8e9f-f6e47fd25777" identifier="/us/usc/t44/s1901"><num value="1901">§ 1901.</num><heading> Definition of Government publication</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">“Government publication” as used in this chapter, means informational matter which is published as an individual document at Government expense, or as required by law.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id122ecb43-e3ef-11ef-8e9f-f6e47fd25777">(<ref href="/us/pl/90/620">Pub. L. 90–620</ref>, <date date="1968-10-22">Oct. 22, 1968</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/82/1283">82 Stat. 1283</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id122ecb44-e3ef-11ef-8e9f-f6e47fd25777">
